{"tid":1353574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要破壞警黑聯盟，我地要有策略","createTime":"2019-07-23T03:45:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T06:55:34.000Z","uid":121113,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9a33d569c6d434f4b00c61cf55a79f485eef49c5","tid":1353574,"uid":121113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:45:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/haUiWoA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhaUiWoA.png&h=f6a6ba94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似玩鬥獸棋咁，我地係老鼠，冇戰鬥力但有速度有數量，獅子老虎一出就走。老黑係收維穩費做野，佢地咁燒錢法都唔會頂到好耐，要拉長戰線同鬥長命，要係舉旗既時候就散，可以再發動過攻勢。<br />\n<br />\n我知道有多手足已經身心俱疲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但我地一定要撐住，一縮就咩都冇架啦！"},{"pid":"110511eec834867dd7ca34db1d2f76bcd1d7e1df","tid":1353574,"uid":121113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:25:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"204457ef327fa811e392bd40c47fe34ba322b924","tid":1353574,"uid":121113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:32:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b57d764bfa6b1e19219e32ece408d455fbdb9bd","tid":1353574,"uid":61161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:33:43.000Z","msg":"同意一縮就無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定不能夠放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f32b1d67f993201b11f7838f7bf96d43742f479","tid":1353574,"uid":121113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:55:34.000Z","msg":"推"}]}